{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7584c678a5","title":"戚本禹王力接见湖北代表座谈纪要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1d345bea2c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":15,"articleId":"7584c678a5","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"王力","id":"20ebde32a6","type":"人物"},{"name":"戚本禹","id":"57434e107b","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"},{"name":"王任重","id":"8b05ac46d8","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"9014e20fdf","name":"戚本禹"},{"id":"fa147b61e7","name":"王力"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"77b7180873","type":"title","text":"戚本禹王力接见湖北代表座谈纪要","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"86d84aa0c3","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹王力接见湖北代表座谈纪要","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"085b12f499","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹  王力","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"25d7b99467","type":"paragraph","text":"1967.05.15","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"acce9b6f81","type":"paragraph","text":"〖时间：1967年5月15日下午3：30分－5：50；地点：政协礼堂东池会议厅。接见单位：新华工、新华农、新湖大、二司、工总、九一三、一始工人造反司令部、黄石代表、天门代表、解放军文艺代表团、卫校代表、三司红色造反团、三司。〗","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d47329a970","type":"paragraph","text":"（在我新华农进来以前，三司以在里面，新华工、新湖大等进来后为了前面的座位和三司吵了起来，因为前面靠桌子的座位每一单位一个记录者，可三司四人座在前面，要他们退下来二个，让工人和解放军他们不让，结果吵了起来。正在吵得很凶的时候，王力、戚本禹进来）","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9fe406d4bf","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们吵，吵我就不接见你们了。（笑着说）","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0e42fe5816","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（坐下后）噢！我见过你们一次，（看见代表们带的袖章后说）新华工、新华农……（这时新华工、新华农、新湖大等单位纷纷献了袖章，新华工代表把“新华工”别在王力同志的军装胸前）。你们给了，你们没有了。上次我说要见你们一次，一直没有时间。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7877e57786","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：（这时武汉军事院校代表进来了）他们都是被抓过的，都进过牢的。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d140a1ca8","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：那不要紧。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9f25399693","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：王力同志来见你们。（介绍王力。）","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"926add6a14","type":"paragraph","text":"王：这是戚本禹同志。（鼓掌）","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cd2820369f","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：我们今天来不能解决任何问题，我们主要是来调查研究的，今天来的有没有两派？","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d4926a7efd","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：有，有三司的！","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"33776c3a93","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：刚才不是在吵架嘛（指他们进来时我们和三司吵架）。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8b639b62f5","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：（介绍刚才吵架的问题）略。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9f30506c3e","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：这点事你们就吵，吵得不可开交，你们的造反精神太大了。（笑）我五点半还有会，现在三点半，开到五点半。你们商量商量怎么开，他们谈听你们的意见。上次已经给记者（谈）过这些问题，武汉的问题主要靠武汉的老百姓解决。我不讲了，你们谈。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"07eed224a5","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：我们先谈一个多钟头，然后请首长指示。（三司指示要两派各谈一半时间。）","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2d6ebd26f1","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们可以多谈点。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"de2c1df885","type":"paragraph","text":"王：你们现在就谈吧！","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3e9db38673","type":"paragraph","text":"武汉代表：首先让我们敬祝我们心中最红最红的红太阳毛主席万寿无疆！万寿无疆！祝林副统帅身体永远健康，永远健康！（鼓掌）","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"80db1f3277","type":"paragraph","text":"王：你叫什么名字？","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d314c12285","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：（介绍）叫某某某。","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fc15ace8ab","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们呆在这里不好，要和群众一起战斗。","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1ffe9471a4","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：首长做指示后，我们马上回去。","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4427d02a5a","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：今天来两派。","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eb127da6e5","type":"paragraph","text":"（武汉革命造反派开始向首长汇报武汉地区资本主义复辟的情况，武汉运动资本主义复辟的表现，革命造反派惨遭残酷镇压，抓、取缔……当谈到军队内部问题，军区机关24个组织被打成反革命组织，抓了200多人，谈到雷达兵问题时。）","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6b7419a917","type":"paragraph","text":"王：雷达兵学校抓人是什么时间？","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0678e5a0a8","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：3月21日","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"84953fb6d9","type":"paragraph","text":"王：这是从2月开始的？（指武汉抓人，搞资本主义复辟。）","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c6f458a9ab","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：二月就开始了。","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"68c15a49a4","type":"paragraph","text":"（同学接着谈，当谈到武汉“二八”声明后，抓人时。）","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d927e95dad","type":"paragraph","text":"王：武汉抓了多少？","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"81999a59d3","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：2600多人。","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c575b939c8","type":"paragraph","text":"（当同学谈到敢死队，抓了人坐牢，又指着敢死队人说，坐牢挨打的人来了。这时敢死队战士起来。戚、王连连点头。）","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3703a4c7af","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：当谈到二司问题时，军区谭（震林）式人物说：学生现在不抓以后要抓。","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a5f99a7b2b","type":"paragraph","text":"（王叹了一口气。）","index":36,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d0b98a8ce1","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：当谈到抓人时，他们还说抓人这是通过江青同志的。","index":37,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"689a7a4e50","type":"paragraph","text":"王：（微笑）哈，县里什么时候开始抓的。","index":38,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b89d96ea46","type":"paragraph","text":"（同学谈韩东山，黄石，天门问题，论韩东山。）","index":39,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d47ede3710","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：我知道。","index":40,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c103bbb755","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：天门二人来等见首长，可是没见到，正准备走时，家里又来人说家里又在抓人。","index":41,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1a11eb5e13","type":"paragraph","text":"（王点了头。）","index":42,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb9316ce6c","type":"paragraph","text":"同志：有的逼的妻离子散，有的急得跑到新疆！","index":43,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"49ac7ba513","type":"paragraph","text":"（王长叹一口气。）","index":44,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"67017ad20c","type":"paragraph","text":"（同学：当谈到某某某地一个人头上钉了三颗钉子，可在上吊后派出所还检查说，这是自杀的，同学说：这不很怪？那有这样事？）","index":45,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"85a8614a91","type":"paragraph","text":"（王摆头。）","index":46,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1d2371c85d","type":"paragraph","text":"（同学谈到绍宇锐时。）","index":47,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6d764dec5d","type":"paragraph","text":"同学（介绍说）：就是武汉的“红卫兵”。","index":48,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2673ee37ca","type":"paragraph","text":"（戚点点头。）","index":49,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6e4d188ed5","type":"paragraph","text":"（同学谈到北京有联动，武汉有几动：特动、军动……）","index":50,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"868598f0e1","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（轻微地）哼！","index":51,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"09361a857b","type":"paragraph","text":"（同志谈到一张保字号的反动大字报，共48张时，念：“周总理是在毛主席身边的定时炸弹……。”）","index":52,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a90df1dda8","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（打断话）不要念了，这我看了。（这时王力接过看）","index":53,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"26d3960400","type":"paragraph","text":"同：三字兵还说王任重“秋后算账”提的过早了，王任重是内部问题。","index":54,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0a4a3d2708","type":"paragraph","text":"（王力轻微地笑。）","index":55,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ad5d3df045","type":"paragraph","text":"同：前几天在北京抓了武汉的特动，他们偷东西，搞到北京来了，","index":56,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"da18fe3cf0","type":"paragraph","text":"（王力笑……。）","index":57,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a16ee2431e","type":"paragraph","text":"同：武汉特动尽是高干子弟组成，王任重儿子，张体学女儿，韩东山儿子。","index":58,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1bab11f4a1","type":"paragraph","text":"（王力点点头。）","index":59,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"75fc45b282","type":"paragraph","text":"同：有的特动说。过去我爸爸用这（铁鞭）打鬼子，我今天用它打思想兵。","index":60,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d0aaddf04b","type":"paragraph","text":"（王力点点头。）","index":61,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b7dc689a72","type":"paragraph","text":"同：解放军战士、武汉军区某些人、武装部都散布“秋后算账”论。","index":62,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f645114208","type":"paragraph","text":"（王力连连点头。）","index":63,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"afc7eceb09","type":"paragraph","text":"（同学谈到武汉军区内有一直站在毛主席路线的一边，如某某某。）","index":64,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"87808b3933","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：谁？","index":65,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ec9c54bcb","type":"paragraph","text":"同：张静。","index":66,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"45a8bfde55","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：是什么人？","index":67,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fe04113543","type":"paragraph","text":"同：湖北军区副政委。","index":68,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"998d062ff7","type":"paragraph","text":"同：军区内坏蛋还造谣，如：通过……（不清）给新华工三点指示。","index":69,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"511dfeb4b0","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（举手）我知道。","index":70,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1c06cf79f1","type":"paragraph","text":"同：江青同志讲话他们篡改（解放军举起材料给戚看）","index":71,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f98a0a62d9","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：点头。","index":72,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2e76940855","type":"paragraph","text":"同：陈再道从北京回汉，武斗不减少，反而增加，三天之内发生150多次。","index":73,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"62cb9c5326","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：点头。","index":74,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9192c7219c","type":"paragraph","text":"同：谈韩东山在黄……（不清）","index":75,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b3794f2c6d","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：算了，不谈了，你们材料我看了。","index":76,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0a1269bf94","type":"paragraph","text":"同：（这时代表讲完了）我讲（新华工）。","index":77,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0b3a7c29dc","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：让不同意见发表，不是有个三司吗？三司在这里！","index":78,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0bde52b058","type":"paragraph","text":"（三司代表发言，略）","index":79,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"efd269a2fa","type":"paragraph","text":"（三司造反派发言，略）","index":80,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e492695ca6","type":"paragraph","text":"（二司发言，略）","index":81,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92c65c7170","type":"paragraph","text":"（新华工、新华农、新湖大联合发言，略）","index":82,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e949148f8d","type":"paragraph","text":"（工人总部发言，略）","index":83,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9d12950b9f","type":"paragraph","text":"（卫生学校发言，略）","index":84,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"993f51ef5b","type":"paragraph","text":"（解放军发言，略）","index":85,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7791eca86c","type":"paragraph","text":"解放军代表：斗他们时，腰弯90度（作姿式）","index":86,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c848158b56","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：点头。","index":87,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"332dde65d7","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们100多少人？","index":88,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b629ab1872","type":"paragraph","text":"解：抓77个人，共164人。","index":89,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"efeb0475df","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：武汉卫生学校。","index":90,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b13a1111a9","type":"paragraph","text":"（解放军代表念一份血书，是一位解放军同志的，念完后交给首长。）","index":91,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"602378e5c7","type":"paragraph","text":"（戚接过血书，王力点点头，接过看。）","index":92,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f13bfd1d5a","type":"paragraph","text":"解：你看直升机散的传单。","index":93,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aae4596376","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：是，是，是……。（接过）","index":94,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ae09e39c39","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：今天我们听了你们很多话，看了很多材料，我们很感谢大家。王力跟我看了材料，听了你们发言，我们有三个意见（不代表中央文革）","index":95,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"34e9c4332a","type":"paragraph","text":"第一、湖北来京工人、学生，赶紧回去到群众中去，参加运动，中央对湖北问题正在调查研究，以后再解决。如果中央再需要你们来反映情况，你们再来。（问：你们来了多少人？）（答：五、六百人）你们赶快回去，因为你们都是勤务员，中央对这个问题，正在研究。","index":96,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cdb6faaef7","type":"paragraph","text":"第二、军区在支工、支农、支左中是有成绩的，但也有缺点错误，这主要是在支左上。现在他们正在改正这些缺点错误，我们和你们都需要再看一看，有缺点错误都要改正，不要越陷越深，改正了就好了。有意见可以说，方式要适当。（指军区）希望你们回去根据中央的指示和湖北的情况形势斗争制定斗争方案、政策。","index":97,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ed549fc30b","type":"paragraph","text":"第三、应当坚决执行军委十条命令、中央对安徽问题五条命令、五条指示。凡是错误地打成反革命的组织，应一律平反。逮捕的，应立即释放。各群众组织应当整风，着重自我批评（王力：着重自我批评。）整顿思想，整顿组织，整顿作风（王力：要掌握斗争的大方向）要掌握斗争的大方向，各群众组织之间的争论只许摆事实，讲道理，不许武斗，不许打砸抢。","index":98,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aa54f1a461","type":"paragraph","text":"一华工同志问：陈再道大字报上街可以不可以？","index":99,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b6f792909e","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：可以采取其他方式，送上门。","index":100,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e078447c3f","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：“打倒陈大麻子”是反动口号。","index":101,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c8d341a0e4","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：以后不要这样喊就行了。我们的意见你们可能不满足，但我们只能讲这么一点，我们还要调查研究，以后解决湖北问题时再请你们来。","index":102,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d141896968","type":"paragraph","text":"（以上稿指示根据首长和我战友对话一节一节合起来的，所以当中有不全之处，有错误我们本人负责，供参考用）","index":103,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7584c678a5","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}